          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Recenser les différentes solutions de garde adoptées par les parents et comprendre la manière dont ils arrivent à concilier leurs vies professionnelle et familiale"
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "To identify the different care solutions adopted by parents and to understand how they reconcile their professional and family life."
